{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Legend of Pamperlotte is a tactical RPG with a unique twist: the &quot;Tactical Combo&quot; system! Depending on your character and class, you can have up to three actions per turn that can be anything! You can run to an enemy, hit him and run away! Or hit an enemy, run and take a potion... The more you use an action per turn, the more efficient it becomes. Another unique feature is the &quot;Turn Again&quot; system. If you defeat an enemy, your combo counter refills and you can act all over again and break havoc in the enemy camp! But beware, the enemy has all those same quirks as you do!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pick your best teams among over 10 classes with 50 different unique skills and techniques. Improve your stats in the skill tree and get to know your teammates with character episodes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a world divided among humans, demons and animals, the war is on the verge of breaking out. Follow Hiro and his friends to prevent the catastrophe and bring peace in the Island of Pamperlotte!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348550/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734712416","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348550/page.bg.jpg?t=1734712416","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348550/f90dfefb9dc6a696e7a36191ab3a40dd5dc1ccb8/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734712416","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348550/f90dfefb9dc6a696e7a36191ab3a40dd5dc1ccb8/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734712416","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Legend of Pamperlotte is a tactical RPG w